"86:14:3" : {s: 86, a: 14, w: 3, r: "هزل", t: "بِٱلْهَزْلِ", l: "هَزْل", lc: 1, tl: "bil-hazli", lb: "ঠাট্টা করা, তামাশা, কৌতুক, রসিকতা",e: "(is) for amusement", b: "পরিহাস", i: "dengan sia-sia/senda gurau", f: 1, rm: "to be thin and lean, useless, fruitless, unprofitable, unproductive, vain, exhausted, joke, talk idle."},
