"86:15:2" : {s: 86, a: 15, w: 2, r: "كيد", t: "يَكِيدُونَ", l: "كِيدُ", lc: 8, tl: "yakīdūna", lb: "চক্রান্ত",e: "are plotting", b: "তারা চক্রান্ত করছে", i: "mereka membuat tipu daya", f: 1, rm: "To be about to, be just on the point of, be well nigh, intend, wish, practise an artful device, desire, contrive/plot/devise such a thing, worked or laboured at or upon anything, to do something clandestinely, to deceive/beguile/circumvent, means of evading/eluding, vomited, emitted fire, had menstrual flux, gave up his spirit."},
